<li><i>A Message From the Sea</i> (1860)</li>
<li><i>Tom Tiddler's Ground</i> (1861)</li>
<li><i>Somebody's Luggage</i> (1862)</li>
<li><i>Mrs. Lirriper's Lodgings</i> (1863)</li>
<li><i>Mrs. Lirriper's Legacy</i> (1864)</li>
<li><i>Doctor Marigold's Prescriptions</i> (1865)</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Mugby_Junction" title="Mugby Junction">Mugby Junction</a></i> (1866)</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/No_Thoroughfare" title="No Thoroughfare">No Thoroughfare</a></i> (1867)</li>
</ul>
</td>
</tr>
